name: Morningrooster
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: morning rooster
des:
The skill will launch a series of thee rooster crowing and will display the image of a rooster on the screen of the deive (provided your device has a screen). The skill will be a random image from an image library. 
The skill is very simple to use and does not require any interaction once it has been launched. The skill will exit automatically at the end of the third rooster crowing.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
